reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product for price. Easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: I am happy to give this a good review. It just fits in my small half bath. Usually I struggle putting these things together and I left it sitting in the box for a week dreading that. Was I surprised! Easy to put together and creatively manufactured. Light weight and I wouldn't put anything great l heavy in it, but I bought it just for tissue and toilet paper storage. It really looks nice. Would recommend buying fur this purpose, it really is cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It works for now.
reviews.reviewText: I moved into a Pre-Mega roll era home and the existing TP holder was problematic. I don’t know what the material is but it feels like super heavy foam board. It went together pretty easy except the little stops for the “hinged” shelf and door. Those little things will drive you crazy. You are going to think they don’t fit but with lots for pushing and wiggling they eventually go into place. There’s no cover for the silver screws but a paint pen in titanium white made them less obnoxious. Another coat might cover them more. I added pictures of before and after. I bought this on a lightening deal so it’s worth what I paid but had I paid full price I would have lost my mind. The door is not hinged nor is the top. They are just pegs in holes. I suspect they will eventually wear down and fail. It’s not heavy duty so don’t expect to put a plant or anything heavy on it. It does hold toilet paper and personal wipes. It also does accommodate a new mega roll of TP which was the whole purpose. I wouldn’t buy another and I would be straight with a friend about the overall value but I’m not mad at it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient and stylish. A must have!
reviews.reviewText: I recently had the opportunity to upgrade my bathroom with a new toilet paper holder, and I must say, it has been a fantastic addition to my restroom. From its functionality to its stylish design, this toilet paper holder stands out as a must-have accessory for any bathroom.First and foremost, the convenience of this toilet paper holder is exceptional. Its well-thought-out design ensures easy and hassle-free access to toilet paper. Whether it’s a traditional roll holder or a wall-mounted holder with a spring-loaded bar, the mechanism allows for smooth and effortless dispensing of toilet paper. This eliminates any frustration or fumbling around when changing the roll, making it a joy to use.The durability and sturdiness of this toilet paper holder are noteworthy. It is typically constructed with high-quality materials such as stainless steel or durable plastic, ensuring its longevity. The holder securely mounts to the wall or stands on its own, providing stability and preventing any wobbling or tipping. Its solid construction gives me confidence that it will withstand regular use and maintain its functionality for years to come.Another aspect to appreciate is the stylish design of this toilet paper holder. It often features sleek and modern aesthetics, seamlessly blending with various bathroom décor styles. The holder’s design enhances the overall look and feel of the bathroom, adding a touch of sophistication and elegance. Whether it’s a minimalist design or a decorative accent, the holder becomes a tasteful addition to the restroom’s overall ambiance.Furthermore, the installation process of this toilet paper holder is usually straightforward. Many models come with all the necessary hardware and clear instructions, making it easy for homeowners to install it themselves. This saves time and money, eliminating the need for professional assistance.Additionally, some toilet paper holders incorporate additional features that add functionality to the overall design. These may include integrated storage shelves or compartments for holding extra rolls, wet wipes, or other bathroom essentials. These thoughtful additions contribute to a clutter-free and organized bathroom space.In conclusion, the convenience, durability, style, and functionality of this toilet paper holder make it an excellent addition to any bathroom. Its user-friendly design, sturdy construction, and attractive aesthetics enhance the overall bathroom experience.I highly recommend this toilet paper holder to anyone looking to upgrade their bathroom and add a touch of convenience and style. Embrace the functionality and elegance it brings, transforming your restroom into a well-organized and visually appealing space.Elevate your bathroom experience with this convenient and stylish toilet paper holder, and enjoy the practicality and aesthetics it offers every time you reach for a roll.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: I wanted some sort of organizer cabinet to put on each side of my makeup vanity in my xl closet since the vanity doesn’t hold many products, but since I wanted them to be narrow most of my options were TP holders. These hold a good bit for their small size and were super easy to assemble. I put prettier knobs on them I got on Amazon. Took off 1 star because doors squeak/ have low quality hinge design. Can’t beat it for the price though.
